        <mxCell id="iZyUO4uBnMnitlq77vA8-13" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;1. Atomic read of target_position and raw_reading. (Atomic ensures they aren&#39;t&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;updating during the reading process).&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Sense check on readings and flag errors.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;3. Convert raw readings.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Apply readings to PID controller.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(Assumes PID is a functional block taking in current &amp;amp; target positions and&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;outputting new target position)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;5. Sense check output and flag errors.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;6. Write output to volatile new_position, set to 0 if errors present.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;(Assume error state means write valve to 0 position)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;7. WDT_kick if no errors, else flag errors&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="430" width="530" x="200" y="380" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="iZyUO4uBnMnitlq77vA8-14" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Main Control RTOS Task&lt;div&gt;Triggered periodically every 1&amp;nbsp;ms (1KHz)&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="240" x="340" y="340" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="iZyUO4uBnMnitlq77vA8-16" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;labelPosition=center;verticalLabelPosition=top;align=center;verticalAlign=bottom;" value="Decoupled Position Writing ISR&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Hardware Timer ISR 50us (20KHZ&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
